title: Veggie packed cottage pie
ingredients: ['1/2 swede', '2 parsnips', '3 carrots', '25g peas', '25g sweetcorn', '25g kidney beans', '25g butter beans', '1 tin of baked beans or chopped tomatoes', '400g minced beef', '4 to 5 medium potatoes', '25g butter', '30ml milk', 'grated cheese', 'oil for frying', 'herbs also can be added for extra flavour']
